<div class="min-h-screen bg-white pt-32 pb-24">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="mb-12">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-gray-600 hover:text-black text-sm font-bold uppercase mb-8 transition-colors">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2">
          <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
        </svg>
        Back Home
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-5xl text-gray-900 mb-4 font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last Updated: February 2, 2026</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">La Hime ("we", "our", or "us") respects the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>
        <p>Please read this policy carefully. If you do not agree with its terms, please do not access our site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Personal Information</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Name, email, shipping address, phone number, and account preferences</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Technical Data</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">IP address, browser type, operating system, and browsing patterns</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Payment Information</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Securely processed through our payment provider (never stored by us)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Process orders and send confirmations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Improve our website and services</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Respond to your inquiries</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Send updates and promotional content (with your consent)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We only share your data with trusted partners who help us operate our business, such as:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-6 list-disc">
          <li>Payment processors</li>
          <li>Shipping carriers</li>
          <li>Hosting providers</li>
          <li>Email marketing services</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600">We never sell your personal information.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-6 list-disc">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>Request corrections to your information</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">For privacy concerns, contact us at:</p>
        <div class="bg-pink-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-pink-100">
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">La Hime Studios</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">contact@lahime.com</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

